    <content>&lt;h1 style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span class="nolink"&gt;Rehab Act Case Studies - Introduction&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: left;"&gt;Let’s further explore the ideas in the Rehab Act by examining some case studies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: left;"&gt;Shiree, Geo, and Corey each have specific learning disabilities. As you listen to each of their cases, consider their protections and responsibilities under the Rehab Act, particularly issues relating to &lt;span class="nolink"&gt;self-disclosure&lt;/span&gt; and self-advocacy.&lt;/p&gt;
